Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:45.80,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Children cling to their coins squeezing out their wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:52.30,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Angels planning disguised with devil's faces
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:59.31,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Children cling on to their very last coins
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.31,0:02:02.27,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Destruction and regeneration
